short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Runebase lightweight wallet and transaction signing client.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Runebase light wallet and transaction signing client.
RunebaseChrome is a light wallet and transaction signing client for decentralized apps (dapps) for the Runebase blockchain. 

- Send and receive RUNES and other RRC223 Tokens.
- Sign transactions sent from decentralized apps
- Delegating (Offline staking)
